@page
@model WebApplicationTest.Pages.IntroductionModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Introduction";
    Layout = "_Layout";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Intro.css">

<div class="full-width-wrapper">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Project Introduction</h1>

            <p>
                Our project features Nana, a voice-interactive VTuber who not only chats naturally like ChatGPT but also offers accurate, personalized answers about our university using a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system. This allows her to respond to questions such as the number of majors offered or the name of the principal with up-to-date and reliable information specific to our school. To make interactions more engaging, we’ve also added custom animations that give Nana a cute and expressive personality, making her not just informative but also fun to talk to!
            </p>
            <p>
                我們的專案是虛擬 VTuber 助理 Nana，她能夠像 ChatGPT 一樣自然地與使用者進行語音互動聊天，但與眾不同的是，她透過「檢索增強生成（RAG）」系統，能夠提供與我們大學相關的準確且個人化的資訊。無論是學校有幾個科系，還是校長是誰，她都能即時回答並提供可靠的資料。為了讓互動更有趣，我們也加入了可愛又富有表情的動畫效果，讓 Nana 不只是資訊豐富的助手，更是陪伴感十足、令人喜愛的虛擬角色！
            </p>
        </div>
     <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="~/css/nana_raise hands.png" alt="Nana">
     </div>
</div>